org.cef.handler

Interface CefRequestHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CefClient, CefRequestHandlerAdapter 

    public interface CefRequestHandler
    Implement this interface to handle events related to browser requests. The methods of this class will be called on the thread indicated.(实现此接口以处理与浏览器请求相关的事件。该类的方法将在指定的线程上调用。)

    • Method Detail

      • getAuthCredentials

        boolean getAuthCredentials(CefBrowser browser,
                           java.lang.String origin_url,
                           boolean isProxy,
                           java.lang.String host,
                           int port,
                           java.lang.String realm,
                           java.lang.String scheme,
                           CefAuthCallback callback)
        Called on the IO thread when the browser needs credentials from the user.(当浏览器需要来自用户的凭据时，在IO线程上调用。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        origin_url - The origin making this authentication request.(origin_url-发出此身份验证请求的原点。)
        isProxy - True if the host is a proxy server.(isProxy—如果主机是代理服务器，则为True。)
        host - Hostname.(host-主机名。)
        port - Port number.(port-端口号。)
        realm - Realm of the request.(realm-请求的域。)
        scheme - Scheme of the request.(scheme-请求的Scheme。)
        callback - Call CefAuthCallback.Continue() when the authentication information is available.(callback-当身份验证信息可用时，调用CefAuthCallback.Continute()。)
        Returns:
        True to continue the request (callback must be executed) or false to cancel.(True表示继续请求（必须执行回调），false表示取消。)

      • getResourceRequestHandler

        CefResourceRequestHandler getResourceRequestHandler(CefBrowser browser,
                                                    CefFrame frame,
                                                    CefRequest request,
                                                    boolean isNavigation,
                                                    boolean isDownload,
                                                    java.lang.String requestInitiator,
                                                    BoolRef disableDefaultHandling)
        Called on the IO thread before a resource request is initiated. The |browser| and |frame| values represent the source of the request. If this callback returns null the same method will be called on the associated CefRequestContextHandler, if any.(在启动资源请求之前在IO线程上调用。|browser|和|frame|值表示请求的来源。如果此回调返回null，则将在关联的CefRequestContextHandler上调用相同的方法（如果有的话）。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        frame - The frame generating the event. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(frame-生成事件的frame。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        request - The request itself. Cannot be modified in this callback. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(request-请求本身。无法在此回调中修改。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        isNavigation - True if the resource request is a navigation.(isNavigation-如果资源请求是导航，则为True。)
        isDownload - True if the resource request is a download.(isDownload-如果资源请求是下载，则为True。)
        requestInitiator - The origin (scheme + domain) of the page that initiated the request.(requestInitiator-发起请求的页面的来源（scheme + domain）。)
        disableDefaultHandling - Set to true to disable default handling of the request, in which case it will need to be handled via CefResourceRequestHandler.getResourceHandler or it will be canceled.(disableDefaultHandling-设置为true可禁用请求的默认处理，在这种情况下，需要通过CefResourceRequestHandler.getResourceHandler进行处理，否则将被取消。)
        Returns:
        A CefResourceRequestHandler instance or null.(CefResourceRequestHandler实例或null。)

      • onBeforeBrowse

        boolean onBeforeBrowse(CefBrowser browser,
                       CefFrame frame,
                       CefRequest request,
                       boolean user_gesture,
                       boolean is_redirect)
        Called on the UI thread before browser navigation. CefLoadHandler.onLoadingStateChange() will be called twice in all cases. If the navigation is allowed CefLoadHandler.onLoadStart() and CefLoadHandler.onLoadEnd() will be called. If the navigation is canceled CefLoadHandler.onLoadError() will be called with an errorCode value of ERR_ABORTED.(在浏览器导航之前在UI线程上调用。在所有情况下，都将调用CefLoadHandler.onLoadingStateChange()两次。如果允许导航，将调用CefLoadHandler.onLoadStart()和CefLoadHandler.onLoadEnd()。如果导航被取消，将调用CefLoadHandler.onLoadError()，其errorCode值为ERR_ABORTED。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        frame - The frame generating the event. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(frame-生成事件的frame。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        request - The request itself. Cannot be modified in this callback. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(request-请求本身。无法在此回调中修改。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        user_gesture - True if the request was initiated by a user gesture.(user_gesture-如果请求是由用户手势发起的，则为True。)
        is_redirect - True if the request was redirected.(is_redirect-如果请求被重定向，则为True。)
        Returns:
        True to cancel the navigation or false to continue.(True表示取消导航，false表示继续。)

      • onCertificateError

        boolean onCertificateError(CefBrowser browser,
                           CefLoadHandler.ErrorCode cert_error,
                           java.lang.String request_url,
                           CefCallback callback)
        Called on the UI thread to handle requests for URLs with an invalid SSL certificate. If "ignore-certificate-errors" command-line switch is set all invalid certificates will be accepted without calling this method.(在UI线程上调用以处理对具有无效SSL证书的URL的请求。如果设置了“ignore-certificate-errors”(忽略证书错误)命令行开关，则将在不调用此方法的情况下接受所有无效证书。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        cert_error - Error code describing the error.(cert_error-描述错误的错误代码。)
        request_url - The requesting URL.(request_url-请求url。)
        callback - Call CefCallback.Continue() either in this method or at a later time to continue or cancel the request. If null the error cannot be recovered from and the request will be canceled automatically.(callback-在此方法中调用CefCallback.Continute()以继续或取消请求。如果为null，则无法从中恢复错误，请求将自动取消。)
        Returns:
        True to handle the request (callback must be executed) or false to reject it.(True表示处理请求（必须执行回调），false表示拒绝请求。)

      • onOpenURLFromTab

        boolean onOpenURLFromTab(CefBrowser browser,
                         CefFrame frame,
                         java.lang.String target_url,
                         boolean user_gesture)
        Called on the UI thread before OnBeforeBrowse in certain limited cases where navigating a new or different browser might be desirable. This includes user-initiated navigation that might open in a special way (e.g. links clicked via middle-click or ctrl + left-click) and certain types of cross-origin navigation initiated from the renderer process (e.g. navigating the top-level frame to/from a file URL).(在某些需要导航新浏览器或不同浏览器的有限情况下，在OnBeforeBrowse之前在UI线程上调用。这包括可能以特殊方式打开的用户启动的导航（例如，通过中键单击或ctrl+左键单击点击的链接），以及从渲染器进程启动的某些类型的跨域导航（例如将顶级frame导航到文件URL/从文件URL导航）。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        frame - The frame generating the event. Instance only valid within the scope of this method(frame-生成事件的frame 。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效)
        user_gesture - True if the request was initiated by a user gesture.(user_gesture-如果请求是由用户手势发起的，则为True。)
        Returns:
        True to cancel navigation or false to continue(True取消导航，false继续)

      • onRenderProcessTerminated

        void onRenderProcessTerminated(CefBrowser browser,
                               CefRequestHandler.TerminationStatus status,
                               int error_code,
                               java.lang.String error_string)
        Called on the browser process UI thread when the render process terminates unexpectedly.(当呈现进程意外终止时，在浏览器进程UI线程上调用。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        status - Indicates how the process was terminated.(status—指示进程终止的方式。)
        error_code - The process error code.(error_code-流程错误代码。)
        error_string - A string description of the error.(error_string -错误的字符串描述。)
